+# Internal — not for investors or external release notes
+
+This folder holds **engineering commit audits** generated from `git log` on `main`. They exist to trace **what landed when**, with commit hashes and merge references.
+
+**Do not** treat these as:
+
+- Investor updates  
+- Customer-facing release notes  
+- A substitute for hand-written entries in **`changelog/`** (repo root)
+
+For external copy, author MDX in the **`wolf-changelog`** repo: **`changelog/wolf-enterprise-frontend/`**, per **`.cursor/commands/changelog.md`**.
